    ElasticUserController
    Created by Ben on 2016-10-27.
    ElasticUserController.AddUserTask
    Called to add a user to elastic search
    ElasticUserController.DeleteUserTask  
    ElasticUserController.EditUserTask
    Async task to update a user in elastic search
    ElasticUserController.FindUserTask
    Async task to search for a user in elastic search and bind it to an object
    LoginActivity
    LoginActivity is where the user enters a username and password so they can access their account.
    LoginMemory
    Creates a save file to tie a user's phone to their account after creating or logging in on the phone.
    NewUserActivity
    User can enter their information and a username They will then go to the next screen to enter vehicle info
    NewVehicleActivity
    This is the class a user will use to input information about their vehicle Once they click register they will then be added as a new user
    User
    Abstract base class for a user of Carrier.
    UserController
    Holds an instance of an user (the user of the app), allows for logging in users with elastic search or memory.
    UsernameTextView
    This TextView is specifically used for usernames.
    UserProfileActivity
    UserProfileActivity allows the user to view their profile information and edit their contact information.
